<div class="title">Summary of 3 Salvia Experiences</div>
<div class="substance">Salvia divinorum</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Itsuoda&Exact=1">Itsuoda</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Itsuoda. "Summary of 3 Salvia Experiences: An Experience with Salvia divinorum (exp3762)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Dec 25, 2001. erowid.org/exp/3762</div>

<br/>



